import Form from "../UI/Form"
import Button from '../UI/Batton'
const ExpenseForm=(props)=>{
    return(
      <form> 
       <Form labelName='Title' id='title' type='text'/>
       <Form labelName='Amount' id='amount' type='number'/>
       <Form labelName='Date' id='date' type='date'/>
     <Button title='отмена'/>
     <Button title='добавить'/>
     </form>
    )
}
export default ExpenseForm
